#  Cardiovascular Disease Prediction

## Overview
This project predicts cardiovascular disease using machine learning models.

##  Dataset
- File: cardio_train.csv
- Separator: ;
- Target: cardio (0 = No disease, 1 = Disease)

##  Features
- Age (converted from days to years)
- Blood Pressure (ap_hi, ap_lo)
- Cholesterol
- Other health attributes

## Workflow
1. Data loading
2. Preprocessing
3. Feature scaling
4. Model training
5. Evaluation

##  Models Used
- Logistic Regression
- Random Forest
- XGBoost

##  Evaluation
- Accuracy Score
- Confusion Matrix

##  How to Run
pip install -r requirements.txt  
python train_model.py

##  Tech Stack
Python, Pandas, Scikit-learn, XGBoost

